      <title></title>
      <link href="/2022/07/14/makefile/"/>
      <url>/2022/07/14/makefile/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="linux下编程目录结构"><a href="#linux下编程目录结构" class="headerlink" title="linux下编程目录结构"></a>linux下编程目录结构</h1><ul><li>src：源码</li><li>incl：头文件</li><li>bin：执行码</li><li>lib：静态&#x2F;动态链接库</li></ul><p>以下的代码编译都是依照这个目录结构</p><h1 id="开始"><a href="#开始" class="headerlink" title="开始"></a>开始</h1><h2 id="零-入门"><a href="#零-入门" class="headerlink" title="零.入门"></a>零.入门</h2><p>先看一个makefile的例子：</p><figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">hello:hello.c</span></span><br><span class="line">gcc -I$&#123;HOME&#125;/incl -c hello.c <span class="comment"># .c包含incl下的头文件</span></span><br><span class="line">gcc -o hello hello.o <span class="comment"># 链接hello.o生成hello二进制包</span></span><br><span class="line">rm -f hello.o <span class="comment"># 删除链接的.o文件</span></span><br><span class="line">mv hello $&#123;HOME&#125;/bin <span class="comment"># 将二进制包移动到特定目录下</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以发现，makefile不就是把编译、链接、删除和移动写成shell脚本吗？没错，去掉第一行，其他代码粘贴到shell脚本里同样可以编译成功，一点问题都没有。但这只是简单的makefile，复杂的makefile还是会看不懂，别着急，咱们来慢慢分析。</p><h2 id="壹-makefile的结构说明"><a href="#壹-makefile的结构说明" class="headerlink" title="壹.makefile的结构说明"></a>壹.makefile的结构说明</h2><p>makefile里面包含了五个东西：变量定义、显式规则、隐晦规则、文件指示和注释。接下来让我一一地介绍</p><ol><li><strong>变量的定义</strong> 在Makefile中我们要定义一系列的变量，变量一般都是字符串，这个有点像C语言中的宏，当Makefile被执行时，其中的变量都会被扩展到相应的引用位置上。</li><li><strong>显式规则</strong> 显式规则说明了，如何生成一个或多的的目标文件。这是由Makefile的书写者明显指出，要生成的文件，文件的依赖文件，生成的命令。 刚才写的疑似shell脚本的Makefile全部都是显示规则。</li><li><strong>隐晦规则</strong> 由于我们的make有自动推导的功能，所以隐晦的规则可以让我们比较粗糙地简略地书写Makefile，这是由make所支持的。</li><li><strong>文件指示</strong> 其包括了三个部分，一个是在一个Makefile中引用另一个Makefile，就像C语言中的include一样。</li><li><strong>注释</strong> Makefile中只有行注释，和UNIX的Shell脚本一样，其注释是用“#”字符，这个就像C&#x2F;C++中的“&#x2F;&#x2F;”一样。如果你要在你的Makefile中使用“#”字符。</li></ol><h2 id="贰-复杂一点的makefile"><a href="#贰-复杂一点的makefile" class="headerlink" title="贰.复杂一点的makefile"></a>贰.复杂一点的makefile</h2><p>根据上面的结构说明，我们对Makefile一层一层的改写，首先是隐晦规则，告诉大家其中一种用法：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 变量的定义</span></span><br><span class="line">INCL=-I<span class="variable">$&#123;HOME&#125;</span>/incl</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#隐含规则</span></span><br><span class="line">.SUFFIXES: .cpp .c <span class="comment"># 将后缀为.cpp和.c的文件分别按下列的规则生成.o文件</span></span><br><span class="line">.cpp.o:</span><br><span class="line">g++ <span class="variable">$&#123;INCL&#125;</span> -c $&lt; <span class="comment"># 变量的使用 $&lt;是一个预定义变量，后面会提到</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">.c.o:</span><br><span class="line">gcc <span class="variable">$&#123;INCL&#125;</span> -c $&lt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># C++编译</span></span><br><span class="line">hellocpp:hellocpp.o <span class="comment"># 文件指示</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 隐含规则已经编译了 g++ $&#123;INCL&#125; -c hello.cpp</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 显式规则</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;开始编译&quot;</span> <span class="comment"># 增加编译日志</span></span><br><span class="line">g++ -o hellocpp hellocpp.o <span class="comment"># 利用.o文件生成二进制可执行文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">rm</span> -f hellocpp.o <span class="comment"># 移除生成的.o文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mv</span> hellocpp <span class="variable">$&#123;HOME&#125;</span>/bin</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;编译结束&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># C编译</span></span><br><span class="line">hello:hello.o</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 隐含规则已经编译了 gcc $&#123;INCL&#125; -c hello.c</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 显式规则</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;开始编译&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">gcc -o hello hello.o</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">rm</span> -f hello.o</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mv</span> hello <span class="variable">$&#123;HOME&#125;</span>/bin</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;编译结束&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>刚才说到了预定义变量，下面是常用的预定义变量的含义：<br><strong>自定义变量</strong></p><ul><li><code>$*</code>不包含扩展名的目标文件名称。</li><li><code>$+</code>所有的依赖文件，以空格分开，并以出现的先后为序，可能包含重复的依赖文件。</li><li><code>$&lt;</code>第一个依赖文件的名称。</li><li><code>$?</code>所有的依赖文件，以空格分开，这些依赖文件的修改日期比目标的创建日期晚。</li><li><code>$@</code>目标的完整名称。</li><li><code>$^</code>所有的依赖文件，以空格分开，不包含重复的依赖文件。</li><li><code>$%</code> 如果目标是归档成员，则该变量表示目标的归档成员名称。</li></ul><p><strong>特殊变量</strong></p><ul><li><code>$(MAKE)</code>：当前make解释器的文件名</li><li><code>$(MAKECMDGOALS)</code>：命令行中指定的目标名（make的命令行参数）</li><li><code>$(MAKEFILE_LIST)</code>：make所需要处理的makefile文件列表，当前makefile的文件名总是位于列表的最后，文件名之间以空格进行分隔</li><li><code>$(MAKE_VERSION)</code>：当前make解释器的版本</li><li><code>$(CURDIR)</code>：当前make解释器的工作目录</li><li><code>$(.VARIABLES)</code>：所有已经定义的变量名列表（预定义变量和自定义变量）</li></ul><p>再对上面的makefile文件扩充一下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#最后形成的Makefile</span></span><br><span class="line">INCL=-I<span class="variable">$&#123;HOME&#125;</span>/incl</span><br><span class="line">BIN=$(HOME)/bin</span><br><span class="line">OBJ1=hellocpp.o</span><br><span class="line">OBJ2=hello.o <span class="comment"># 定义了更多的变量</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">.SUFFIXES: .cpp .c</span><br><span class="line">.cpp.o:</span><br><span class="line">g++ <span class="variable">$&#123;INCL&#125;</span> -c $&lt; <span class="comment"># 生成.o文件的方式：将第一次看到的.cpp文件，通过引入的库文件，生成.o文件</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">.c.o:</span><br><span class="line">gcc <span class="variable">$&#123;INCL&#125;</span> -c $&lt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">all: hellocpp hello</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#C++编译</span></span><br><span class="line">hellocpp:<span class="variable">$&#123;OBJ1&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;============开始编译============&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">g++ -o <span class="variable">$@</span> $?</span><br><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">rm</span> -f <span class="variable">$&#123;OBJ1&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">mv</span> <span class="variable">$@</span> <span class="variable">$&#123;BIN&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;============编译结束============&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#C编译</span></span><br><span class="line">hello:<span class="variable">$&#123;OBJ2&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;============开始编译============&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">gcc -o <span class="variable">$@</span> $?</span><br><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">rm</span> -f <span class="variable">$&#123;OBJ2&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">mv</span> <span class="variable">$@</span> <span class="variable">$&#123;BIN&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;============编译结束============&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
